Dialogue: 0,0:01:33.11,0:01:35.63,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那麼  我要到傍晚的時候才能回來
Dialogue: 0,0:01:35.84,0:01:38.45,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,中午純就去叫個外賣回來吃吧
Dialogue: 0,0:01:38.87,0:01:39.87,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喔！
Dialogue: 0,0:01:40.44,0:01:41.55,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,知道了的說
Dialogue: 0,0:01:41.79,0:01:44.84,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,雖然是在放暑假  不過紀還是很忙呢
Dialogue: 0,0:01:45.00,0:01:47.25,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,快到比賽了  所以一直要去參加社團訓練
Dialogue: 0,0:01:47.49,0:01:48.31,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,社團訓練？
Dialogue: 0,0:01:48.63,0:01:49.70,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,棍球訓練哦
Dialogue: 0,0:01:49.83,0:01:50.46,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哦？
Dialogue: 0,0:01:50.84,0:01:52.51,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那麼我走了
Dialogue: 0,0:01:54.13,0:01:56.02,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我偷偷的告訴你的說
Dialogue: 0,0:01:56.34,0:01:59.70,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那是用那個棒狀的武器攻擊敵人的頭頂
Dialogue: 0,0:01:59.97,0:02:03.95,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一直戰鬥到對方無法動彈為止的死亡遊戲的說！
Dialogue: 0,0:02:04.69,0:02:08.67,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,快再多看看即將面對這一切的紀的臉龐的說哦！
Dialogue: 0,0:02:09.33,0:02:10.98,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,拜託你們看家了呢
Dialogue: 0,0:02:11.20,0:02:17.55,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,紀！要加油啊！不要死！努力啊！……
Dialogue: 0,0:02:17.95,0:02:21.70,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,萬歲！萬歲！萬歲——！
Dialogue: 0,0:02:34.42,0:02:35.21,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我說啊
Dialogue: 0,0:02:36.26,0:02:37.00,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什麼？
Dialogue: 0,0:02:37.45,0:02:40.90,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你平時是從哪裡找到那些書的啊？
Dialogue: 0,0:02:41.19,0:02:43.40,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是放在那間有鏡子的房間裡的
Dialogue: 0,0:02:44.15,0:02:45.16,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哦…
Dialogue: 0,0:02:54.04,0:02:55.77,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我一點都看不懂
Dialogue: 0,0:02:56.18,0:02:57.96,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那是德語
Dialogue: 0,0:02:58.41,0:03:00.92,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,煉金術和潛意識心理學
Dialogue: 0,0:03:01.48,0:03:03.79,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只要有興趣的話你也應該可以看得懂的
Dialogue: 0,0:03:03.98,0:03:04.34,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,為什麼？
Dialogue: 0,0:03:05.25,0:03:07.31,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你可是我的媒介啊
Dialogue: 0,0:03:07.63,0:03:10.62,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,與我共享著很多能力
Dialogue: 0,0:03:11.15,0:03:12.67,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只要集中精神
Dialogue: 0,0:03:12.88,0:03:15.65,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,書中的內容自然會流入你的腦海
Dialogue: 0,0:03:15.98,0:03:17.99,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可我連英文書都看不懂啊
Dialogue: 0,0:03:18.53,0:03:21.00,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那是因為你的集中力還不夠
Dialogue: 0,0:03:26.82,0:03:28.47,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,還是看不懂啊
Dialogue: 0,0:03:28.98,0:03:30.03,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,剛才我是騙你的
Dialogue: 0,0:03:31.29,0:03:32.09,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真愚蠢啊
Dialogue: 0,0:03:32.50,0:03:34.95,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你這傢伙…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:35.48,0:03:38.06,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你這個騙人的人偶！還總是這麼盛氣凌人的！
Dialogue: 0,0:03:38.35,0:03:40.40,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼可能這麼簡單就能被你讀懂呢？
Dialogue: 0,0:03:40.50,0:03:41.34,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你說什麼？
Dialogue: 0,0:03:42.17,0:03:43.40,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,感覺真奇怪
Dialogue: 0,0:03:43.77,0:03:47.05,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大概是想把人偶齊聚於這個時代\N所帶來的沉重氣氛轉換一下的說
Dialogue: 0,0:03:47.32,0:03:49.58,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,能夠放鬆自己  她真是堅強呢
Dialogue: 0,0:03:50.19,0:03:51.56,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也許會是個強大的敵人
Dialogue: 0,0:03:51.72,0:03:54.30,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你在說什麼的說啊！什麼「敵人」的…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:54.78,0:03:59.15,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,人偶聚齊  就是愛麗絲遊戲開始的標誌
Dialogue: 0,0:03:59.53,0:04:02.27,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,說不定什麼時候就要必須相互戰鬥
Dialogue: 0,0:04:02.80,0:04:04.15,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這是父親大人的…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:04.20,0:04:06.41,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這種事我才不管的說！
Dialogue: 0,0:04:06.68,0:04:09.87,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,雖然翠星石也非常喜歡父親大人
Dialogue: 0,0:04:10.14,0:04:13.28,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是  也一樣非常喜歡蒼星石還有真紅她們的說
Dialogue: 0,0:04:13.59,0:04:18.20,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果不得不搶奪蒼星石的薔薇聖母的話
Dialogue: 0,0:04:18.48,0:04:21.62,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,翠星石就不想成為愛麗絲了的說
Dialogue: 0,0:04:22.72,0:04:24.88,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,想和大家永遠永遠在一起的說…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:25.98,0:04:29.66,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果  薔薇水晶盯上蒼星石的話
Dialogue: 0,0:04:29.89,0:04:32.85,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,翠星石一定會保護蒼星石的說
Dialogue: 0,0:04:34.14,0:04:36.32,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要快點找一個主人
Dialogue: 0,0:04:46.04,0:04:47.80,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,帶上這個走吧
Dialogue: 0,0:04:48.09,0:04:50.28,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,今天好像會下雨呢
Dialogue: 0,0:04:50.76,0:04:52.37,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,謝謝的說
Dialogue: 0,0:04:52.78,0:04:55.70,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那個…嗯…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:56.59,0:04:58.78,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,長時間以來承蒙照顧的說
Dialogue: 0,0:04:59.48,0:05:00.38,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那個…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:00.88,0:05:03.90,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可是我如果不去找自己的主人的話…那個…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:04.16,0:05:06.07,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不要這樣啊  翠星石
Dialogue: 0,0:05:06.34,0:05:08.55,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這又不是永遠分別
Dialogue: 0,0:05:09.92,0:05:10.77,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,爺爺…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:11.12,0:05:13.04,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就是啊  小翠
Dialogue: 0,0:05:13.30,0:05:17.02,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,呃…「小不點人類」先生的家也就在附近
Dialogue: 0,0:05:17.37,0:05:18.03,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,隨時都可以…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:18.15,0:05:21.04,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂  喂  人家叫作「純」啊
Dialogue: 0,0:05:21.36,0:05:22.13,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哎呀  真是的
Dialogue: 0,0:05:22.81,0:05:25.42,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,傳染上小翠的說法了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:27.50,0:05:28.34,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,純？
Dialogue: 0,0:05:28.73,0:05:32.22,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你說要去尋找主人  就是去純那裡吧？
Dialogue: 0,0:05:32.24,0:05:34.29,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,誰…誰要和純那種傢伙…！
Dialogue: 0,0:05:34.66,0:05:35.28,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不是嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:05:49.16,0:05:51.89,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要給她上發條嗎？還是不給她上？
Dialogue: 0,0:05:52.13,0:05:55.56,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也許從現在就會獲得一個可愛的妹妹的…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:56.31,0:05:58.77,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊——又掛斷了的說！
Dialogue: 0,0:06:05.43,0:06:08.58,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是的  全都是不明白的人的說！
Dialogue: 0,0:06:16.79,0:06:18.98,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你就乖乖的到純那裡去吧
Dialogue: 0,0:06:21.10,0:06:26.35,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯  既然蒼星石都這麼說了  我就去看看的說吧…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:30.21,0:06:31.24,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是的
Dialogue: 0,0:06:31.53,0:06:35.01,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小不點人類要在廁所裡躲到什麼時候的說啊！
Dialogue: 0,0:06:35.18,0:06:38.35,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,純最近總是會在廁所裡看雜誌
Dialogue: 0,0:06:38.62,0:06:39.86,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,每次都很久才會出來
Dialogue: 0,0:06:40.06,0:06:43.86,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哦…那裡確實是個漂亮的地方呢
Dialogue: 0,0:06:44.44,0:06:45.84,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,能夠令人安下心來呢
Dialogue: 0,0:06:46.10,0:06:49.18,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不過  如果說看雜誌的話還會是這樣嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:06:51.58,0:06:54.21,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我要去使勁敲廁所的門的說！
Dialogue: 0,0:06:56.82,0:06:57.34,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,咦
Dialogue: 0,0:06:57.61,0:06:59.29,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喔  你來了啊？
Dialogue: 0,0:06:59.48,0:07:01.82,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊…不…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:02.10,0:07:04.62,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,其實翠星石正在尋找主人
Dialogue: 0,0:07:04.69,0:07:05.25,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不是…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:05.52,0:07:07.64,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是嗎？所以就來找純？
Dialogue: 0,0:07:07.69,0:07:08.80,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯？我嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:07:09.07,0:07:11.64,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那…個  那個  那個…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:11.89,0:07:14.64,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,翠星石也很喜歡純嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:07:14.80,0:07:15.49,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊？
Dialogue: 0,0:07:17.83,0:07:20.80,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒有這回事的說！我才不想被賣掉的說！
Dialogue: 0,0:07:23.99,0:07:25.09,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,翠星石！
Dialogue: 0,0:07:26.75,0:07:28.29,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那傢伙怎麼回事啊
Dialogue: 0,0:07:31.43,0:07:32.52,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,翠星石！
Dialogue: 0,0:07:50.42,0:07:51.59,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哼  哼  哼
Dialogue: 0,0:07:51.84,0:07:54.76,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,想要高興的滾來滾去  也就只有趁現在了吧？
Dialogue: 0,0:07:55.26,0:07:58.14,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,今天我金絲雀一定要…嗯？
Dialogue: 0,0:08:03.36,0:08:03.96,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,咦？
Dialogue: 0,0:08:19.14,0:08:20.03,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼辦
Dialogue: 0,0:08:20.58,0:08:22.80,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,暫時先回爺爺家吧
Dialogue: 0,0:08:23.00,0:08:26.73,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不要的說  這樣灰溜溜地逃回去也太難看了的說
Dialogue: 0,0:08:26.92,0:08:28.56,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那麼就去純家
Dialogue: 0,0:08:28.73,0:08:29.86,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那我也不願意的說！
Dialogue: 0,0:08:30.44,0:08:31.59,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那  要怎麼辦？
Dialogue: 0,0:08:42.34,0:08:42.95,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,純？
Dialogue: 0,0:08:48.55,0:08:49.63,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真糟糕啊
Dialogue: 0,0:08:51.91,0:08:54.18,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,蒼  蒼星石去拿給他的說！
Dialogue: 0,0:08:54.36,0:08:56.08,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是翠星石提出來的吧？
Dialogue: 0,0:08:56.26,0:08:58.33,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是的  怎麼這麼扭捏的說！
Dialogue: 0,0:08:58.56,0:08:59.76,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,扭捏的是…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:59.91,0:09:01.91,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂  你們在做什麼啊？
Dialogue: 0,0:09:09.42,0:09:10.41,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那個…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:13.16,0:09:15.93,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我有兩把的  所以這個…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:16.24,0:09:18.14,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真  真是不好意思
Dialogue: 0,0:09:20.85,0:09:22.75,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是的  既然小不點人類都找到這裡
Dialogue: 0,0:09:22.92,0:09:24.89,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我也就逃不掉了的說
Dialogue: 0,0:09:25.14,0:09:25.58,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什麼？
Dialogue: 0,0:09:25.91,0:09:28.22,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要是不和翠星石訂下契約的話
Dialogue: 0,0:09:28.43,0:09:30.35,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一定不會放棄的說呢
Dialogue: 0,0:09:30.56,0:09:31.34,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是沒辦法  那就…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:31.47,0:09:32.00,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂  等一下！
Dialogue: 0,0:09:32.18,0:09:34.43,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,誰說想要和你訂契約了！
Dialogue: 0,0:09:35.30,0:09:36.90,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,翠星石才沒有墮落到
Dialogue: 0,0:09:36.94,0:09:39.67,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要骯髒的小不點人類作主人的說！
Dialogue: 0,0:09:39.75,0:09:40.41,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你說什麼？
Dialogue: 0,0:09:41.82,0:09:45.10,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我絕對不要和你這種傢伙訂契約的說！
Dialogue: 0,0:09:45.56,0:09:47.30,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你這個骯髒噁心的臭小鬼！
Dialogue: 0,0:09:48.46,0:09:52.22,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可惡…那個性格惡劣的人偶…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:52.91,0:09:54.09,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,翠星石…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:58.54,0:10:01.26,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,討厭的純  我不管了的說
Dialogue: 0,0:10:03.55,0:10:06.50,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗚哇…看起來要糟糕了吧？
Dialogue: 0,0:10:08.01,0:10:10.77,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那個就是奇怪的第七人偶吧？
Dialogue: 0,0:10:11.32,0:10:13.57,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,她居然在附近出沒…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:14.23,0:10:16.21,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是計劃的一大失誤吧？
Dialogue: 0,0:10:16.73,0:10:19.42,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這樣下去的話  會被那傢伙先搶走…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:19.81,0:10:21.86,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,被我抓到了的說  你這頑固的傢伙
Dialogue: 0,0:10:25.44,0:10:30.01,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,翠星石在家裡經常幫奶奶的忙
Dialogue: 0,0:10:30.32,0:10:30.92,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,咦…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:35.66,0:10:38.60,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,翠星石很擅長沏烘焙茶
Dialogue: 0,0:10:38.97,0:10:40.24,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不是紅茶啊
Dialogue: 0,0:10:41.00,0:10:43.20,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,爺爺喜歡喝烘焙茶的
Dialogue: 0,0:10:43.47,0:10:44.84,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以翠星石…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:44.93,0:10:48.07,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你在背著人家瞎說些什麼的說啊！
Dialogue: 0,0:10:49.39,0:10:52.15,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我說你  稍微藏起來一點啊
Dialogue: 0,0:10:52.32,0:10:53.77,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不是說這個的時候的說！
Dialogue: 0,0:10:54.36,0:10:55.84,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真紅她們有危險了！
Dialogue: 0,0:10:56.38,0:10:56.90,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,咦？
Dialogue: 0,0:10:58.65,0:11:04.42,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,下～雨  下～雨  下～雨
Dialogue: 0,0:11:05.00,0:11:06.34,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我說  真紅
Dialogue: 0,0:11:06.70,0:11:09.55,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你覺得雨變成果汁比較好呢？
Dialogue: 0,0:11:10.25,0:11:13.32,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,還是變成牛奶比較好？
Dialogue: 0,0:11:14.43,0:11:15.16,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我說
Dialogue: 0,0:11:16.06,0:11:17.09,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,噗…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:18.66,0:11:21.19,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真無聊哦——
Dialogue: 0,0:11:24.14,0:11:24.69,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊！
Dialogue: 0,0:11:28.48,0:11:28.89,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,呀！
Dialogue: 0,0:11:33.87,0:11:34.82,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,薔薇水晶！
Dialogue: 0,0:11:58.11,0:11:58.86,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真紅！
Dialogue: 0,0:12:05.65,0:12:08.18,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真紅…雛莓…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:16.43,0:12:18.41,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一定是在有鏡子的房間裡的說！
Dialogue: 0,0:12:18.46,0:12:22.56,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,明明說了是水窪  怎麼就是不明白呢？
Dialogue: 0,0:12:22.64,0:12:23.06,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,咦？
Dialogue: 0,0:12:23.51,0:12:24.58,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,水窪啦
Dialogue: 0,0:12:24.85,0:12:25.79,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,水窪？
Dialogue: 0,0:12:29.69,0:12:30.45,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是這個嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:12:38.99,0:12:39.74,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,呀！
Dialogue: 0,0:12:41.22,0:12:41.90,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這是…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:42.31,0:12:43.53,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,n之領域啊！
Dialogue: 0,0:12:56.64,0:12:57.28,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,翠星石！
Dialogue: 0,0:12:57.34,0:12:57.92,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂！
Dialogue: 0,0:13:03.57,0:13:06.43,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,屁股…有點濕了吧？
Dialogue: 0,0:13:08.27,0:13:09.01,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這裡是…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:09.21,0:13:12.67,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂喂  你這女人想做什麼啊！
Dialogue: 0,0:13:15.19,0:13:18.10,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好像不是薔薇水晶的領域的說
Dialogue: 0,0:13:25.48,0:13:26.12,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,純！
Dialogue: 0,0:13:26.34,0:13:28.10,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,為什麼小不點人類也…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:28.75,0:13:30.90,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你會拖後腿而已的說！
Dialogue: 0,0:13:31.18,0:13:34.10,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我要做什麼不關你們的事吧
Dialogue: 0,0:13:34.14,0:13:34.83,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊
Dialogue: 0,0:13:36.00,0:13:36.83,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,純！
Dialogue: 0,0:13:37.05,0:13:37.92,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,雛莓
Dialogue: 0,0:13:39.17,0:13:39.99,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真紅
Dialogue: 0,0:13:40.11,0:13:42.91,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,太好了  你們兩個都沒事呢
Dialogue: 0,0:13:43.54,0:13:44.63,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,薔薇水晶呢？
Dialogue: 0,0:13:45.65,0:13:47.13,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,追丟了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:47.70,0:13:50.90,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我們也不知怎麼回事就到了這裡
Dialogue: 0,0:13:52.13,0:13:53.30,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真紅
Dialogue: 0,0:13:54.31,0:13:55.40,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,雛莓
Dialogue: 0,0:13:55.85,0:13:57.16,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,翠星石
Dialogue: 0,0:13:57.60,0:13:59.04,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,蒼星石
Dialogue: 0,0:13:58.20,0:13:59.05,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這個聲音是…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:59.51,0:14:00.51,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,金絲雀
Dialogue: 0,0:14:01.10,0:14:04.09,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,還有  薔薇水晶
Dialogue: 0,0:14:05.88,0:14:06.82,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,她也…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:07.57,0:14:11.67,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,被傀儡線牽引而來的人偶們
Dialogue: 0,0:14:12.24,0:14:16.21,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你們所編織而成的是名為命運的掛毯
Dialogue: 0,0:14:16.49,0:14:20.68,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,故事的主角們現在齊集於此
Dialogue: 0,0:14:21.30,0:14:25.67,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,愛麗絲遊戲終於開幕了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:16.72,0:15:17.68,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,停下來…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:22.16,0:15:24.09,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小雛樣子的人偶被…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:27.50,0:15:28.25,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊！
Dialogue: 0,0:15:31.39,0:15:33.21,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這種興趣也太糟糕了的說！
Dialogue: 0,0:15:33.80,0:15:35.16,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,愛麗絲遊戲…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:35.34,0:15:35.82,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,咦？
Dialogue: 0,0:15:49.29,0:15:52.13,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,停下來…停下來…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:58.92,0:16:00.94,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,停下來…停下來…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:01.29,0:16:05.27,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小金人偶  站起來  還可以站起來吧？
Dialogue: 0,0:16:09.87,0:16:11.44,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果愛麗絲遊戲開始了的話
Dialogue: 0,0:16:11.92,0:16:13.76,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,總有一天  我們將會…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:17.58,0:16:18.87,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,別開玩笑了的說！
Dialogue: 0,0:16:19.12,0:16:20.79,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真紅！小不點莓！
Dialogue: 0,0:16:21.07,0:16:23.20,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不要被那種猴戲搞亂陣腳的說！
Dialogue: 0,0:16:23.41,0:16:24.20,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,說得對！
Dialogue: 0,0:16:25.41,0:16:27.89,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那種東西和你們不是完全不同的嗎！
Dialogue: 0,0:16:28.45,0:16:29.18,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,純…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:29.86,0:16:31.95,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這種事情不可能發生的！
Dialogue: 0,0:16:37.65,0:16:41.26,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那麼  就讓我們開始吧
Dialogue: 0,0:16:42.33,0:16:44.34,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真正的愛麗絲遊戲
Dialogue: 0,0:16:50.87,0:16:52.16,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,等  等一下
Dialogue: 0,0:16:52.40,0:16:53.52,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有點糟糕吧？
Dialogue: 0,0:17:11.63,0:17:12.48,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,翠星石！
Dialogue: 0,0:17:16.99,0:17:17.61,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真紅！
Dialogue: 0,0:17:30.16,0:17:31.08,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:32.71,0:17:34.42,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真紅  你…！
Dialogue: 0,0:17:43.26,0:17:44.41,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,蒼星石！
Dialogue: 0,0:17:59.06,0:17:59.78,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,純…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:08.89,0:18:09.71,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可惡…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:14.30,0:18:14.96,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,純…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:15.61,0:18:16.32,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,來吧！
Dialogue: 0,0:18:17.51,0:18:18.85,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,來訂下契約吧！
Dialogue: 0,0:18:20.31,0:18:21.00,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,純…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:40.33,0:18:41.05,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼了？
Dialogue: 0,0:18:53.05,0:18:54.97,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,水之夢——！
Dialogue: 0,0:19:04.48,0:19:07.47,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只要有了媒介在  你這種傢伙根本不放在眼裡的說！
Dialogue: 0,0:19:07.88,0:19:09.90,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好  好熱啊…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:15.53,0:19:16.17,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,快逃吧！
Dialogue: 0,0:19:16.42,0:19:16.97,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,咦？
Dialogue: 0,0:19:17.36,0:19:19.47,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真紅！蒼星石！要走了！
Dialogue: 0,0:19:20.51,0:19:21.06,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,純…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:21.22,0:19:22.16,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真紅！走吧！
Dialogue: 0,0:19:45.42,0:19:46.50,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我們的…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:47.36,0:19:48.84,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,愛麗絲遊戲…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:53.91,0:19:56.59,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,替我向爺爺奶奶問好的說
Dialogue: 0,0:19:56.79,0:19:58.34,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,還  還有
Dialogue: 0,0:19:58.63,0:20:01.00,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,廁所的電燈泡快壞了  要換一個
Dialogue: 0,0:20:01.16,0:20:04.94,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,還有  就是  我還會時常回去住一住的…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:05.12,0:20:06.08,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,還  還有就是…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:06.11,0:20:06.90,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,翠星石
Dialogue: 0,0:20:07.30,0:20:07.87,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,咦？
Dialogue: 0,0:20:12.86,0:20:14.61,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,明天我也會來玩的
Dialogue: 0,0:20:14.99,0:20:16.38,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,到時候再和我說吧
Dialogue: 0,0:20:17.36,0:20:18.76,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,蒼星石…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:19.80,0:20:21.09,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我們什麼時候都能再見的
Dialogue: 0,0:20:21.87,0:20:22.93,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因為我們是姐妹嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:20:30.98,0:20:33.61,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,每天每天都要來玩的說
Dialogue: 0,0:20:33.99,0:20:35.45,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一定要來的說
Dialogue: 0,0:20:35.84,0:20:36.41,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:21:07.46,0:21:08.66,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你幹什麼呢？
Dialogue: 0,0:21:08.84,0:21:10.50,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我在看書的說
Dialogue: 0,0:21:10.67,0:21:12.40,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,看數學參考書？
Dialogue: 0,0:21:12.62,0:21:13.47,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是的說
Dialogue: 0,0:21:13.67,0:21:14.22,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊？
Dialogue: 0,0:21:14.98,0:21:19.40,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,每天睡覺之前奶奶都會給我們唸書的
Dialogue: 0,0:21:28.53,0:21:33.26,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這個X乘以3之後就等於4了  所以X…
Dialogue: 0,0:21:34.82,0:21:35.58,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有趣嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:21:35.89,0:21:37.31,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,很有趣的說！
Dialogue: 0,0:21:37.59,0:21:40.95,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這個叫X的很有看頭的說！
Dialogue: 0,0:21:41.12,0:21:42.02,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喔…
Dialogue: 0,0:21:43.40,0:21:44.84,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,接著念下面的說！
Dialogue: 0,0:21:45.21,0:21:50.19,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯…要求這個X的值以及角度…
Dialogue: 0,0:21:50.23,0:21:51.18,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯！嗯！
Dialogue: 0,0:21:51.46,0:21:54.24,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗚——！嗚——！
Dialogue: 0,0:21:54.42,0:21:56.41,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,竟然把我一個人丟下
Dialogue: 0,0:21:56.51,0:21:58.79,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,多麼殘忍的傢伙們呀！
Dialogue: 0,0:21:58.97,0:22:01.58,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗚——我的屁股——
Dialogue: 0,0:22:04.23,0:22:08.96,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,總有一天我要報復的吧——
Dialogue: 0,0:23:41.15,0:23:41.83,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,太好啦！
Dialogue: 0,0:23:42.04,0:23:45.91,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,翠星石也和純契約了  也要住在一起了！
Dialogue: 0,0:23:46.05,0:23:48.56,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這種事本來是絕對會拒絕的說哦
Dialogue: 0,0:23:48.63,0:23:49.55,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是沒辦法的說
Dialogue: 0,0:23:49.58,0:23:50.64,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以作為補償～
Dialogue: 0,0:23:50.78,0:23:52.53,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,雛莓的地盤就全都歸我了的說
Dialogue: 0,0:23:52.63,0:23:54.13,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好了  快給我讓開的說
Dialogue: 0,0:23:54.23,0:23:54.92,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,咦？
Dialogue: 0,0:23:55.03,0:23:58.00,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,還有  早上要在我起來之前準備好我的早餐的說
Dialogue: 0,0:23:58.09,0:24:00.42,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗚  比真紅還難伺候哦
Dialogue: 0,0:24:00.55,0:24:02.63,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,下集  薔薇少女  夢見
Dialogue: 0,0:24:02.89,0:24:05.68,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那旋律宛如夢中所見哦
